
<!--
		put in dtor order
		=> transform before anything else
		=> render before entity/particles/...
		=> collider before bodies
		
		if a component does not exist it does not affect the program
		since it wont be created (it's not registered)
		
		the names here should be the same as the register
		
		components:
			- position
			- scale
			- orientation
			- speed
			- forward
			- playershootlifetime
			- playercontrol
			- lifespan
			- render
			- entity
			- particles
			- enemylifetime
			- collider
			- rigidbody
			- collisions
			- explosion
			- sound2d
			- sound3d
			- soundlistener
			- scenenodeanimation
			- meshanimation
		
-->

